name: Rocket Racers (Tulenväki Productions)
description:
Race through the asteroid field with ever increasing speeds.
Solo for Mobile and Desktop.
Coop with you friend on Mobile.

Playable also in liluo.io.

Made for GDevelop Weekend Game Jam #2: Mobile edition.

Coding - Rami Niemi
SFX - Rami Niemi
Speech - Rami Niemi using xVASynth
Graphics - Rami Niemi, Teemu Vestovuo
Lens Flares - Sleeper Games

Music tracks are Free to use from Aim to Head Official
Alkaline - Aim to Head
Cain - Aim to Head
